urlLink White House Sway Is Seen in E.P.A. Response to 9/11 : "      White House Sway Is Seen in E.P.A. Response to 9/11    By JENNIFER 8. LEE        ASHINGTON, Aug. 8 %u2014 An investigation by the Environmental Protection Agency's inspector general into official statements about air quality after the collapse of the World Trade Center has found that White House officials instructed the agency to be less alarming and more reassuring to the public in the first few days after the attack. "